<li>Martin Richards, C. Whitby-Strevens, <i>BCPL, the language and its compiler</i> (Cambridge University Press, 1980) <a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521286816" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-521-28681-6</a></li>
